Nightmare race description: klingon

Number of arms: 2
Number of legs: 2
Number of fingers per hand: 5
Special limb info:
    None.

Night vision: Above average

Language: Tlinghan

Genetic traits:
Klingons are very strong and sturdy, and highly dexterous for their 
size.  Although they are not generally considered pleasing to look at,
they are not considered hideous either.  They are niether wise nor bright.

Physical description:
Klingons are a huge fighting race.  Although their skin colour varies from
tan to very dark, all Klingons have dark hair which is culturally worn long.
They have ridges upon their foreheads which are as unique to each Klingon
as a fingerprint is to a human.

Most common occupation: Fighter
